title: Kafe de luxe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Busy yet cozy space situated in central Vaxjo's oldest wood house. Organic, local produce and an international spicy kitchen are main parts of the restaurant. Both lunch and dinner vegetarian dishes (and some vegan) are served as well as in-house-made cakes and cookies in addition to hot and cold drinks. Weekends the basement music venue and nightclub is open until late.
